rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0001
rows.name:
For it to not even flinch when a Divine Beast bumps into it...
the World Tree is an endless source of curiosity!

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Since it's called the World Tree, it's also a subject
of botanical study.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd love to take young Ellie there for some
fieldwork inside it someday.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Ellie is a kid in this town who looks
after the trees...

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0005
rows.name:
He's got a pretty good eye for plants,
and what's more, he says his dream is to be a botanist.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I thought I needed to be a guidepost
for a kid like Ellie.
